\v 5 \x - \xo 9:5-7 \xt Aisaia 14:29-31; Jeremaia 47:1-7; Esekiel 25:15-17; Joel 3:4-8; Amos 1:6-8; Sefanaia 2:4-7\x*Eght…® Askelon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba bizir kam…®n ganigh bar atiatigham. Me uaghan kuram iniam, eght…® men nguibam, gumazamiziba g…®n an ikian kogham. Eght…® Gasaba uaghan bizir kam…®n gant…®, os…®mt…®zir ekiam me batogham, mati amizim borim batamin m…®zazim a bato. Eght…® men atrivim aremegham. Eght…® Ekronba uaghan bizir kam…®n gan…®va os…®mt…®zir ekiar kam iniam, mati amizim borim batasa m…®zazim isi. Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Tairba ti men akuragham. Ez…® puvat…®, me bar ikuvigham.  
