\v 7 Eght…® Filistian ikiav…®ra itir varazira, me nan gumazamizibar m…®n otivigh Judan anababar tong…®n ikiam. Jebusia\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Jebusia, me Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n nguazir ghueba. Devit g…®n taun Jerusalem iniam, Jebusia Israelia ko iti. N…® Josua 15:63…®n gan.\f* fom…®ram amiz…® mogh…®n, Ekronba dat…®r…®gh…®n nan gumazamizibar ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, me ghuziba itir as…®zir tuzibar aman kogh…®va, uaghan Judaba ataghizir dagheba, me dar aman kogham.\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Judaba as…®zim isams…® faragh bar derav…®rama an ghuzim ruegh…®va g…®n a isamigh aneremam. Ez…® Filistiaba arazir kam gamir puvat…®gha, Moses osiriz…® mogh…®n me God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. (N…® vez…®n kabar gan: Jenesis 9:4; Ofa Gami 3:17 ko 7:26-27; God…®n Araziba 12:16 ko 15:23.) Ikiav…®ra Itir God kagh kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, me as…®zim ghuziba sara ik…®t…® me aneman a men anogoroke.\f* 
