\c 12  
\s1 God g…®n ua Jerusalem iniam 
\p  
\v 1 Kar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia bagha an…®ngizim. Ikiav…®ra Itir God overiam ko, nguazim…®n ingarigha, gumazamizibar ingarigha, ik…®r…®m…®rir angam…®ra itim me gan…®ngi. A kamagh…®n m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúK…® Jerusalem damight…® a wain itir kav…®n m…®n otogham. Eght…® kantrin igharazir an borogh…®n ikia, a gas…®ghas…®ghasava amiba, me mati gumazir wain…®n kav…®n kam amegha onganiziba. Me m…®dorozim bagh Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®va, me Judan nguibar dozir igharaziba bar da sara ek…®arugham.  
\v 3 Dughiar kam otogh g…®vaght…®, k…® Jerusalem damight…®ma a dag…®ar bar os…®mt…®zim…®n m…®n otogham. Eght…® kantriba bar a ko m…®soghs…® uari akuvagh, me uari ikuvigham, mati gumazim dag…®ar os…®mt…®zir kam fava m…®zazim isi.  
\v 4 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® dughiar kam…®n apanibar hoziabar amight…®, da bar atiatigham, eght…® dagh is…®n apiazir gumaziba bar onganigham. K…® Judabagh eghuva, men apanibar hoziabar amight…® dar damaziba bar okavigham.  
\v 5 Eght…® Judan gumazir dapaniba bizir kam…®n ganigh, uarira uariv k…®m suam, ‚ÄòGod, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a gavgavim uan gumazamizir Jerusalem…®n itibagh an…®ngi.‚Äô\f + \fr 12:5 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n k…® Judan gumazir dapanibar amight…®, me mati tuzim dafogha isi mogh…®n, o mati wit…®n azenir bar m…®s…®ngizim dafogha isia m…®zariaba zui. Eght…® kantrin men borogh…®n itiba da bar g…®vagham. Eght…® Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiamra, a itir danganimra ik…®v…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Judan m…®dorozir gumazibar amight…®, me faragh…®v…®ra apaniba ab…®nigh ziar ekiam iniam. Eght…® Devit uan ovavir boriba ko, Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba, men ziar ekiam, Judan gumazamizibar ziar ekiam gafighan kogham.  
\v 8 Dughiar kam…®n k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba geghuvam, mati gumazim oram…®n uab…® modi. K…® gavgavim me dan…®ngt…®, gumazir m…®dorozibar gavgavizir puvat…®ziba, me Atrivim Devit…®n m…®n gavgavigham. Eght…® Devit…®n ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba, me, men gumazir dapanibar ikiam, eght…® me mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel o God uab…®, egh me, me geghuvam.  
\v 9 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, kantrin igharazir Jerusalem ko m…®soghava amiba, k…® bar dagh as…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir afuzim…®n ruazir aremezim, me g…®n an aghuimazim…®n ikiam 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 12:10-14 \xt Jeremaia 31:9; Akar Mogomem 1:7\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Devit…®n ovaviba ko, Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamizir igharaziba, k…® me damut…®, me uan navir averiabar aven apangkuvir arazim ko, God ko m…®geir arazim…®n g…®n mangam. Egh gumazir me afuzim…®n ruazim, me an ganigh a bagh bar puv aziam. Mati gumazim otarir ivariamra itima, an aremez…®, an a bagha puv…®ram azi mogh…®n, me bar osemegh puv…®ram aziam.\f + \fr 12:10 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Ekiam faragha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Israelia Godra rua, egha a g…®n akam giragha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, me gumazir igharazim b…®raz…®, an areme. Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, God uab…® me bagh amadazir gumazim me a m…®soghez…® an areme. Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, faragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar igharazim iti, ez…® me g…®n mong akam pazav an osiri. Jon 19:37 ko Akar Mogomem 1:7 m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kamning, Krais…®n otozir bizim…®n ababanim.\f* 
\v 11 Dughiar kam…®n Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n azirakar bar ekiam an aven otogham. Mati, me fom…®ra Megidon danganir zarim…®n ikia, asem Hadatrimon bagha bar puv…®ram azi mogh…®n, men azirakam an m…®rara mangam.\f + \fr 12:11 \ft Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Hadatrimon, an aser mam…®n ziam. Gumazamizir an ziam feba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia ghaze, an azenibar zurara dar dughiar vam…®ran aremegham, eght…® me a bagh puv…®ram aziam. Egha g…®n, me ghaze, a uam angam…®ra iti.\f* 
\v 12-14 Ik…®ziba bar, me vaghvagh an aghuimazim…®n ik…®va aziam. Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazi uari baghv…®ra ik…®t…®, Natan…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazi uari baghv…®ra ik…®t…®, Livain ik…®zim…®n adarazi uari baghv…®ra ik…®t…®, Simein adarazir ik…®zim uari baghv…®ra ik…®t…®, eght…® ik…®zir igharaziba bar mogh…®ram aziam. Ik…®ziba bar vaghvagh uari akuvagham, eght…® men gumaziba uari baghv…®ra ik…®va azit…®ma, men amiziba uari baghv…®ra ik…®va aziam. 
\c 13  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Onger Akaba 51:2; 51:7; Aisaia 1:16-18; Esekiel 36:25; Jon 1:29\x*‚ÄúDughiar kam otoght…® k…® mozir d…®pam damight…® an anang otogh iram. Devit…®n ovaviba ko, Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamizir igharaziba, me god…®n ifavaribar ziaba fava, arazir m…®z…®r…®zir av…®ribagh ami. Eght…® d…®par kam men arazir kuraba ruam.‚Äù 
\s1 Akam inigha izir gumazir ifariba g…®vagham 
\p  
\v 2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dughiar kam…®n god…®n ifavarir marvir guaba nguazir kam…®n da batuegham, eght…® gumazitam uam a dagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Egh uaghan akam inigha izir ifavarir gumaziba ko, duar m…®z…®r…®ziba, k…® nguazir kam…®n da batuegham.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt God…®n Araziba 18:20\x*Eght…® akam inigha izir gumazitam, God…®n akam…®n m…®n ifavarir akabav k…®mt…®, an amebam ko, afeziam uaning kamagh a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® uan akar ifavarim…®n gun m…®gei. Kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® aremegham.‚Äô Gumazir kam akar ifavarir kam m…®k…®mt…®, an amebam ko, an afeziam afuzim…®n a b…®raght…®ma, an aremegham.  
\v 4 Dughiar kam…®n, akam inigha izir gumazir ifavariba, men tav uan irebabar m…®n garir biziba bagh aghumsigh, bar akongeghan kogham. Me God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar korotiatam aghuan kogham. Egh God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar arazitam gumazamiziba gifar…®s…®, a damighan kogham. Puvat…®gham.  
\v 5 A kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòK…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim puvat…®. K…® azenibar ingarir gumazim. K…® gumazir igharazim…®n pura ingangarir gumazir k…®nim.‚Äô\f + \fr 13:5 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 6 Eght…® gumazitam kamagh…®n an azaragham, ‚ÄòKar manmagh…®n amizir duar kurim n…®n evarim…®n iti?‚Äô Eght…® a ifar suam, ‚ÄòK…® uan namakam…®n d…®penim…®n a ini.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù\f + \fr 13:6 \ft Akam inigha izir gumazir maba, me afuam inigha pura tintinibar uan m…®karzim aghorir arazim…®n g…®nt…®si. (N…® 1 Atriviba 18:28…®n ganigh.) Egha gumaziba an evarim…®n afuar d…®ghoribar ababanibar ganigha me fo, kar akam akurir gumazim. Ez…® a me gifara ghaze, puvat…®.\f* 
\s1 God sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazim m…®gei 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 13:7 \xt Matyu 26:31; Mak 14:27\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgavim Bar Itim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nan m…®dorozir sabam, d…®kavigh na bagh uan namakam, a sipsipbar garir gumazim, a m…®sueght…®ma, sipsipba tintinim…®n aregham. Kamagh…®ra, mati gumazim sipsip…®n nguzibav sosi mogh…®n, k…® uan gumazamizibav sogham.  
\v 8 Egh k…® kantrin kam…®n gumazamiziba me tuiraght…®, me 3plan ik…®zibar otogham. Eght…® k…® ik…®zir pumuning m…®sueght…® aning aremegham. Eght…® ik…®zir abuananam ikiam.  
\v 9 Eght…® ik…®zir itir kam, a nan damazim…®n zueghs…®, k…® a damu ganigham, mati me silvaba ko, gol…®n m…®neziba batueghasa, avim…®n da tuema da isi. Eght…® me na ko m…®k…®mt…®, k…® men m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragham. Egh k…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa nan gumazamiziba.‚Äô Eght…® me kamagh…®n na m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòN…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® en God.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 14  
\s1 Apaniba iz…® Jerusalemia ko m…®sogham 
\p  
\v 1 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n kotiar ekiam…®n dughiam izam. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n apaniba iz…® Jerusalem…®n dag…®aba ko biziba iniam. Me ian damazibar bizir aghuir kaba tuiragh uari dan…®ngam.  
\v 2 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® kantrin igharazibar m…®dorozir gumaziba bar da inight…®, me iz…® Jerusalem m…®sogham. Me Jerusalemia ab…®nigh bizir d…®penim…®n itiba bar ada inigham. Egh arazir otuaribar amizibar amuam. Egh gumazamizir kabar nar mam inigh mang…®t…®, me kantrin igharazibar kalabus…®n ikiam. Eght…® men akuar mam Jerusalem ateghan kogham, me an ik…®v…®ra ikiam.  
\v 3 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God zurara m…®dorozibagh ami mogh…®n, a d…®kavigh mang…® kantrin kabav sogham.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 14:4 \xt Esekiel 47:1-10; Maika 1:3-4; Habakuk 3:6; Sekaraia 4:7; 14:8\x*M…®dorozim otivir dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God d…®kavigh, Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am gis…®n tugh…®v ikiam. Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am a Jerusalem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n iti. Eght…® Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am tong…®ra bigh…®va, akuar pumuning otoght…®, m…®ghs…®ar akua tam mang…® saut…®n amadaghan otoght…®, an akuar vuem not…®n amadaghan ikiam. Eght…® aning…®n t…®zimning…®n danganir zarir ekiam ikiam.  
\v 5 Danganir zarir kam, a bar mang…®, Asal…®n nguibam…®n otogham. Eght…® ia ar…® danganir zarir kam…®n mang…® vong…®n otogham. Fom…®ra Usia Judan atrivim…®n itima, m…®k…®mk…®zir ekiam otoz…® ian ovaviba arez…® mogh…®n, ia zuam…®ram aregham. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan God, uan enselba bar ada inigh ia bagh izam.  
\v 6 Eght…® angazangarim aruem…®n dughiamra otivan kogham. Puvat…®.\f + \fr 14:6 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 7 \x - \xo 14:7 \xt Aisaia 60:19; Matyu 24:36; Akar Mogomem 21:23; 22:5\x*Am…®nim p…®rir dughiam…®n, angazangarim isi mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® arueba ko, d…®magaribar dughiaba g…®vagham, da uam otivan kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…®ra, bizir otivamin kabar dughiam g…®fo. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 14:8 \xt Esekiel 47:1; Joel 3:18; Jon 7:38; Akar Mogomem 22:1\x*Dughiar kam…®n, d…®par aghuir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim an…®dim Jerusalem…®n ikegh ivemar mangam, eght…® an tam Amangs…®zim Itir D…®par Akarem…®n mang…®t…®ma, an tam Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n mangam. D…®par kam dughiabar ivemar mamagh…®ra ikiam, an amoziba ko, aruebar dughiam…®n ivemar mamagh…®ra ikiam. A bar dakeghan kogham.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 14:9 \xt Aisaia 2:2-4; 45:21-24; Sekaraia 9:9; 14:16-17\x*Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God nguazir kam…®n kantriba bar dagh ativagh dar Atrivim…®n ikiam. Eght…® a bar uab…®ra, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra ziar vam…®ra a dar…®gh, an ziam fam. 
\p  
\v 10 Eght…® nguazir Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itim, a vorogh…®ra itir danganir zarim…®n otogham, a not…®n amadaghan Geban nguibar ekiam…®n ikegh, mang…® saut…®n amadaghan Rimon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogham. Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiamra m…®ghs…®atam gis…®n ikiam. Eght…® Jerusalem av…®namin d…®vazir bar m…®tiar gavgavim, a fom…®ra ikez…® mogh…®ra, a kamagh…®ra ikiam. Jerusalem…®n d…®vazim, a Benjamin…®n Tiar Akam…®n ikegh mang…®, M…®kebam…®n Tiar Akam…®n otogham, danganir kam tiar akar mam fom…®ra iti. Egh ababanir m…®taghniar Hananel…®n Tauan ikegh mangamim, a mang…® me atrivim bagha wain…®n ingarir danganim…®n otogham.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 14:11 \xt Akar Mogomem 22:3\x*Eght…® Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba danganir kam…®n derav…®ra ikiam, eght…® bizitam ua me gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 12 Kantrin Jerusalem ko m…®soziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ar…®mariar bar kuram me bagh anemangam. Ar…®mariar kam kamak…®n, gumazamiziba angam…®ra ik…®t…®, men m…®karziba ko damaziba ko m…®zeba bar kuright…®, dar kuriba pura iram.  
\v 13 Dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God me damight…®, me atiating…®va onganigham. Egh me uarir borogh…®n itir darazir suigh…®va, uariv sogh…®va ar…®ghiram.  
\v 14 Eght…® Judan gumaziba Jerusalem…®n akurvaghs…® m…®sogham, eght…® an gumazamiziba ikuvighan kogham. Egh me kantrin igharaziba bar, me da, men gol ko silva ko korotiar av…®rir aghuiba inigham.  
\v 15 Eght…® men apanibar averpeniba itir danganim…®n, ar…®mariar kurar kamra men hoziaba ko kamelba ko donkiba ko as…®zir guar igharaziba bativam. 
\s1 Kantriba bar men gumazamiziba God…®n ziam fam 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 14:16 \xt Ofa Gami 23:39-43\x*Judaba uan apaniba ab…®raght…®, men apanir m…®keagh…®r…®ziba, me azenibar zurara Jerusalem…®n iz…®va Atrivim…®n ziam fam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim. Egh me Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiam…®n aven ikiam.  
\v 17 Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizitaba, atrivim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, me an ziam fan aghuaght…®, amozim men nguazim gizan kogham.  
\v 18 Eght…® Isipia, Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiam…®n aven ik…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n izam fan aghuaght…®ma, faragha isam…®n mangan aghuazir darazi inizir ar…®mariar kurar kamra, Isipia uaghan a iniam.  
\v 19 Isipia ko Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, me uaghan Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiam…®n mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fan aghuagh…®va, me uaghara uan arazir kuraba bagh ivezir kurar magh garim iniam. 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 14:20 \xt Ua Me Ini 28:36-38; Aisaia 23:18; Esekiel 46:20\x*Dughiar kam…®n, me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gham, bizir kaba, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizir zuezibara. Hoziabar f…®ribagh ikezir belon muziariba, da uaghan osizirim kamagh…®n dar ikiam, ‚ÄúBizir kaba, da bar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n bizir zueziba.‚Äù Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itir m…®ner k…®niba, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n guiz…®n zuezir bizibar otivam, mati itarir ekiar me ofa damuasa as…®zir ghuziba isa ofa gamir dakozim gingem.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Esekiel 44:9; Sefanaia 1:11; Sekaraia 9:8\x*Eght…® Jerusalemia ko, Judabar d…®peniba bar dar itir m…®ner k…®niba, da uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n damazim…®n zuezir bizibar ikiam. Eght…® g…®n gumazamiziba ofabar amus…®, pura m…®ner kaba inigh dar ofabar amuamin as…®zir tuziba avigham. Dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n D…®penim…®n bizibagh iveza, da amadir gumaziba ua ikian kogham.